ğŸ› Challenges & Fixes
Issue 1: Forwarder Not Sending Logs
Root Cause: SplunkForwarder service was not running
Fix: Started service and verified active connection using:
splunk list forward-server 
Issue 2: Security Log Access Denied
Root Cause: Domain user lacked permission to read Security logs
Fix: Added user to Event Log Readers group
Issue 3: Logs Dropped
Root Cause: Target index not created on Splunk Enterprise
Fix: Created wineventlog index
